text: Justin Tranter (born 16 June 1980) is an American musician and jewellery designer. He has co-wrote songs for Julia Michaels. == History == Justin Tranter was born on 16 June 1980. He has co-wrote Julia Michaels' "Issues" (2017). == Discography == === Production and songwriting credits === * Julia Michaels - "Issues" Category:American pop musicians Category:Musicians from Illinois Category:1980 births Category:Living people
